Class Bird

java.lang.Object
Inheritance.Bird
Direct Known Subclasses:
Waterfowl
public class Bird extends Object
The Bird class serves as a base class for all bird-related subclasses, such as "Waterfowl" and "Duck". Provides common properties and behaviors for birds, such as flying, laying eggs, and making noise. Subclasses can extend this class to add specific functionality.
